  "steps": [
    "Weigh 25 mg ( 0.025 g ) of Chloramphenicol.",
    "Add the chloramphenicol to a 1.5 mL tube.",
    "Add 100% ethanol to the 1mL level on the tube.",
    "Vortex the tube for 5 seconds, repeat 3 times.",
    "Store the tube in the -20°C freezer."
